OL,7,FDerek George Lammey, 60, has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to 18 months in jail for
OL,9,Fintimidation offence connected to an
OL,10,Falleged "show of strength" in the Pitt
OL,11,FPark area of East Belfast in February
OL,12,F2021.
OL,14,FIt was the Crown's case that Lammy was
OL,15,Fpart of an intimidating crowd of 40
OL,16,Fmasked loyalists who'd gathered
OL,17,Fshouting threats outside of a
OL,18,Fcommunity centre.
